    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alien plants convert sunlight into energy. Infuse broken components with that power to spark new life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/787bbd6c9d35ecdb0ab019d03db8691c.poster.avif?t=1759477658\" width=380 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/787bbd6c9d35ecdb0ab019d03db8691c.webm?t=1759477658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your scanner to find hidden tracks below the surface and draw energy along them to spread life to new areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/c523ea2b3514ea73042059144bd147ed.poster.avif?t=1759477658\" width=380 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/c523ea2b3514ea73042059144bd147ed.webm?t=1759477658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and plant seed pods and watch the interplay of nature and technology unfold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/2706ca19f11d24c5233eca02fb28b018.poster.avif?t=1759477658\" width=380 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735350/extras/2706ca19f11d24c5233eca02fb28b018.webm?t=1759477658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This charming solar-punk adventure rewards thoughtful interaction with its vibrant world. The unfolding story is as unique as the way you play.</p>",
